  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "61406766-82dd-47b0-bfd1-5f582bf3448b",
    "name": "SmartAppointmentApp",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the Smart Appointment System microservices.\n\n**Services:**\n- Auth Service (port 4001)\n- Doctor Service (port 4003)\n- Appointment Service (port 4004)\n- API Gateway (port 3000)\n\n**Quick Start:**\n1. Run the `login` request under AuthService — it auto-sets `accessToken`, `refreshToken`, and `userId` collection variables.\n2. All protected routes use `{{accessToken}}` automatically via the collection-level Bearer auth.\n3. After creating a doctor, copy the `_id` into the `doctorId` variable. After booking, copy into `appointmentId`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "49212612",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/49212612-61406766-82dd-47b0-bfd1-5f582bf3448b?source=collection_link"
  },
